<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ - بَابُ الشِّينِ الْمُعْجَمَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٠٦ - شَبِيهُ - أَوْ شَبَهُ - الشَّيْءُ مُنْجَذِبٌ إِلَيْهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هُوَ مِنْ كَلامِ الْغَزَالِيِّ فِي الإِحْيَاءِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٠٧ - الشِّتَاءُ شِدَّةٌ وَلَوْ كَانَ رَخَاءً<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢٠٨ - شَرُّ الْحَيَاةِ وَلا الْمَمَاتِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ بَلْ قَالَ ابْنُ حَجَرٍ إِنَّهُ مِنْ كَلامِ بَعْضِ الْقُدَمَاءِ مِنَ الْحُكَمَاءِ وَلَيْسَ عَلَى إِطْلاقِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢٠٩ - شَرُّ الرِّعَاءِ الْحُطَمَةُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>